{"tid":162000,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"（喜訊）不能備份遊戲記錄, 任天堂 Switch 一死即一無所有","createTime":"2017-03-19T02:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T08:58:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e16f7e68a4844105c931f5796b41b655c5da261","tid":162000,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T02:53:48.000Z","msg":"三月 7, 2017<br />\n不能備份遊戲記錄, 任天堂 Switch 一死即一無所有<br />\n蝦哥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/IMAG1696.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2FIMAG1696.jpg&h=3ad9d1c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n分享推文Pin郵件<br />\n打機好多時值錢的不是遊戲 , 因為遊戲光碟壞了可再買 , 但遊戲的記錄(Save)就是見證自己玩過而留下的事跡 , 是玩家留下血肉的證據 . 不過如果你有玩任天堂 Switch , 你就需要小心保養好你的遊戲機 (編按:沒用的 , 電子產品說死就死 , 不留情面.)<br />\n<br />\nSwitch 機身上有 microSD 卡槽 , 不過原來是無法備份 , 所以有卡槽都沒有用 . 而官方亦已經證實 Switch 的遊戲記錄只會儲存在 Switch 的主機內 , 暫時完全沒有方法可以複製過去其他媒介(包括 microSD) . 更值得留意的是 Switch 只有 32GB ROM , 實際可用只有 26GB , 加上一些遊戲升級檔等 , 空間可以很快就用完 . 萬一用光之後 , 你想再玩新遊戲就需要刪除之前的遊戲記錄及檔案 , 十萬個痛苦啊 ."},{"pid":"9a9a91245b662365c0531419177f87f8ddd5c7b4","tid":162000,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9109b9e7d6f73a3ea849429a71c2cf99001672","tid":162000,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc2cb0c881d496a84c4f08bb720d1c923182178","tid":162000,"uid":40321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:48:49.000Z","msg":"有返game boy既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad960f13752af8a61d3c9531b134e9837250226","tid":162000,"uid":24211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"h